    "author_association": "OWNER",
    "body": "\"I don’t like that the tag is up to the implementation to generate. You end up signing arbitrary data, where the signature could be reused elsewhere. Better to derive a key via a KDF and a unique but exact tag specified in the standard.\"\r\n\r\nhttps://twitter.com/rootlabs/status/975216701468889088\r\n"
